Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还用问吗？想听心爱的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开玩笑的 收到联络
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}听好 这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}蠢毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}内容很简单 听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}绝对别和比布利欧家族会扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}家族会？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不然的话 就把那件事告诉你的王子殿下
Comment: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}OP
